{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckbox"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkbox is a UI element that allows to select multiple options from a set of mutually non exclusive choices."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Checkbox that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a checkbox to be displayed."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:isReadOnly:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:tableName:bundle:isError:isReadOnly:)"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/body"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Particular cases","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must b